videos.headline: Braden Smith's no-look pass sets up Zach Edey for a big jam
videos.description: Purdue extends its lead over Penn State thanks to Braden Smith's assist to Zach Edey for a slam.

videos.headline: Purdue wins Big Ten championship after Penn State's late turnover
